[TITLE]Bugfixes
Fixed an issue where items that would discard for Professor Pete would also discard for Mystery Toon
Fixed an issue where using White-Out during some real-time boss fights would cause the \"I'm Stuck!\" to remain disabled
Fixed a non-functional wall in the Molten Mint"
